      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This driver\u2019s example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed Dual-VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing. The high-revving powerplant breathes through individual throttle bodies, providing immediate throttle response and that signature metallic rasp. Handling is sharpened by an upgraded coilover suspension and a factory M-Variable differential lock for superior mechanical grip. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the chassis remains taut and the drivetrain is exceptionally dialed. Recent fluid analysis confirms the health of the rod bearings. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the backroads.",
